## Agent procedure reference

Procedure **bodies** live under [`.reinguard/procedure/`](../../.reinguard/procedure/) (SSOT). **Cursor entry:** [`rgd-next.md`](../commands/rgd-next.md) — `rgd context build` then open the mapped procedure (ADR-0013). Other `.cursor/commands/` files (e.g. `issue-create`) are exceptions for GitHub-only flows.

Use `gh` CLI for observation (`gh issue view`, `gh pr view`, `gh pr checks`, etc.) until full `rgd observe` coverage.

